    <item>
      <title>拜登特别顾问的文字记录对敏锐度的看法褒贬不一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/biden-transcript-paints-mixed-picture-of-president-s-acuity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统接受司法部特别检察官罗伯特·胡尔采访的文字记录描绘了他的精神敏锐度的好坏参半的画面，而共和党人在 2024 年大选中将这一问题作为一个大棒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/biden-transcript-paints-mixed-picture-of-president-s-acuity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>真主党向以色列发射火箭弹，战斗不断升级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/hezbollah-fires-wave-of-missiles-at-israel-in-escalating-battle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[真主党向以色列军事基地发射了一百多枚导弹，这是该黎巴嫩组织近几个月来最严重的袭击之一，有可能使本已一触即发的冲突升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/hezbollah-fires-wave-of-missiles-at-israel-in-escalating-battle</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 10:24:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚称中国提议取消220%的葡萄酒关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-issues-draft-to-end-australia-wine-tariffs-winemaker-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚葡萄酒公司和立法者表示，中国提议取消对该国葡萄酒的惩罚性关税，这表明随着两国寻求加强关系，为期三年的贸易争端即将结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-issues-draft-to-end-australia-wine-tariffs-winemaker-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 09:39:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>海地总理因暴力团伙和前科犯争夺权力而辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/haiti-prime-minister-ariel-henry-resigns-as-violence-escalates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[海地总理阿里尔·亨利表示，在经历了数周的混乱和暴力之后，他将辞职，因为他对权力的控制有所松动，并对华盛顿针对这个西半球最贫穷国家的战略提出了挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/haiti-prime-minister-ariel-henry-resigns-as-violence-escalates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 04:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约州称特朗普应在欺诈案上诉期间缴纳全额保释</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/ny-says-trump-should-post-bond-for-full-fraud-fine-before-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约总检察长对唐纳德·特朗普声称他可能必须亏本出售房产才能获得对 4.54 亿美元民事欺诈罚款提出上诉所需的保证金的说法提出了异议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/ny-says-trump-should-post-bond-for-full-fraud-fine-before-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 00:54:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟观察员称取消塞内加尔投票的新提议可能会失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/barred-senegal-opposition-leader-urges-top-court-to-cancel-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位专家表示，塞内加尔反对派政治家卡里姆·韦德向法院提出的取消选举的请求不太可能成功，这消除了人们对进一步拖延的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/barred-senegal-opposition-leader-urges-top-court-to-cancel-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 00:09:44 GMT</pubDate>
